	* maintaining.texi (Advanced C-x v v): Use fileset terminology.
	(VC With A Merging VCS, VC Change Log): Add xref to VC Pull node.
	(VC Pull): Mention vc-log-incoming.
	(Log Buffer): Add CVS/RCS only disclaimer.

